   "source": [
    "# GT HCR ROIs absent in pairwise-unmixed CSV\n",
    "\n",
    "For every subject with a `HCR_<sid>_pairwise-unmixing_*` dataset,\n",
    "quantify how many GT-matched HCR ROIs are missing from\n",
    "`unmixed_all_cells.csv`, where they sit in depth, and how the v5d\n",
    "ROI-quality classifier scores them.\n",
    "\n",
    "Subjects with unmixing now include the newly added **790322**."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
